---
title: "Vico Agent — 决策与执行时序"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor U as 👤 用户
    participant AL as AgentLoop
    participant DT as 复杂度检测
    participant PL as Planner LLM
    participant CTX as 上下文 (ContextManager)
    participant EL as Executor LLM
    participant TK as 工具引擎 (asyncio.gather)
    participant UI as 终端渲染器

    U->>AL: run("给电脑做体检")
    AL->>CTX: add_user_message(...)
    AL->>DT: _is_complex_task("给电脑做体检")
    DT-->>AL: True (命中关键词 "体检")

    Note over AL,PL: ── Phase 1：规划阶段 ──

    AL->>PL: stream(LLMRequest, tools=None)
    Note right of PL: 无工具权限<br/>max_tokens=2048
    PL-->>UI: ReasoningChunk → on_thinking()
    PL-->>AL: TextChunk → plan 文本
    AL->>UI: on_plan(plan_text) → 渲染 Plan 面板
    AL->>CTX: add_assistant_message(plan_summary)

    Note over AL,TK: ── Phase 2：执行循环（Turn 1）──

    AL->>EL: stream(LLMRequest, tools=tool_defs)
    Note right of EL: 携带 plan_summary<br/>批量工具调用 Prompt
    EL-->>UI: ReasoningChunk → on_thinking()
    EL-->>AL: ToolCallChunk × 6 (并行批次)
    AL->>UI: on_tool_call() × 6 → 显示 spinner

    AL->>TK: asyncio.gather(execute × 6)
    Note right of TK: bash: sw_vers<br/>bash: sysctl ...<br/>bash: df -h<br/>bash: netstat ...<br/>bash: ifconfig ...<br/>bash: pmset -g batt
    TK-->>AL: ToolResult × 6
    AL->>UI: on_tool_result() × 6 → 更新状态行
    AL->>CTX: add_tool_result() × 6

    Note over AL,TK: ── Phase 2：执行循环（Turn 2）──

    AL->>EL: stream(LLMRequest, tools=tool_defs)
    EL-->>AL: ToolCallChunk × 3 (下一批次)
    AL->>TK: asyncio.gather(execute × 3)
    Note right of TK: bash: 防火墙状态<br/>bash: 系统日志<br/>bash: 启动项检查
    TK-->>AL: ToolResult × 3
    AL->>CTX: add_tool_result() × 3

    Note over AL,EL: ── Phase 2：最终输出（Turn 3）──

    AL->>EL: stream(LLMRequest, tools=tool_defs)
    EL-->>AL: TextChunk → 最终报告
    EL-->>AL: DoneChunk (无工具调用)
    AL->>UI: on_text() + flush() → 渲染 Markdown 报告

    AL-->>U: 体检完成 ✅
